#Blood Lactate
```{r}
BlaLMM <- lmer(Bla ~ Time_Point + BFR + Speed + Time_Point*BFR + Time_Point*Speed + (1|Participant), data = main_df2)
summary(BlaLMM)
pairwise_Bla <- emmeans(BlaLMM, pairwise ~ Time_Point + BFR + Speed + Time_Point*BFR + Time_Point*Speed, adjust="holm")
pairwise_Bla
```

```{r}
tab_model(BlaLMM)
```
